== 製作 ==

=== 發展 ===

2011年10月，[[索尼影視娛樂|索尼影業]]取得了艾薩克森小說《[[賈伯斯傳|賈伯斯傳]]》的電影改編權，並聘請[[艾倫·索金|艾倫·索金]]來為小說進行改編<ref>{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2011/10/sony-pictures-acquiring-apple-icon-steven-jobs-book-for-feature-film-180666 |title=Sony Pictures Acquiring New Steve Jobs Biography For Major Feature Film |last=Fleming Jr |first=Mike |publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |date=2011-10-07 |accessdate=2016-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160807184300/http://deadline.com/2011/10/sony-pictures-acquiring-apple-icon-steven-jobs-book-for-feature-film-180666/ |archive-date=2016-08-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Armitage |first=Hugh |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a347359/social-network-aaron-sorkin-to-write-steve-jobs-biopic.html |title='Social Network' Aaron Sorkin to write Steve Jobs biopic? |work=[[數碼間諜|Digital Spy]] |date=2011-10-25 |accessdate=2016-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160826175441/http://www.digitalspy.com/movies/news/a347359/social-network-aaron-sorkin-to-write-steve-jobs-biopic/ |archive-date=2016-08-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。11月，傳出[[喬治·克隆尼|喬治·克隆尼]]與[[諾亞·懷利|諾亞·懷利]]（曾在1999年電視電影《[[微軟英雄|微軟英雄]]》中飾演賈伯斯）將飾演賈伯斯的消息<ref>{{cite web |last=West |first=Kelly |url=http://www.cinemablend.com/new/George-Clooney-Looking-Play-Steve-Jobs-Biopic-27973.html |title=Is George Clooney Looking To Play Steve Jobs In The Biopic? |website=CinemaBlend |date=2011-11-18 |accessdate=2016-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303204716/http://www.cinemablend.com/new/George-Clooney-Looking-Play-Steve-Jobs-Biopic-27973.html |archive-date=2016-03-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2012年5月，索金證實他正在撰寫劇本<ref name="Mike Fleming Jr">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2012/05/aaron-sorkin-to-script-steve-jobs-based-on-walter-isaacson-book-for-sony-272953/ |title=Aaron Sorkin To Script 'Steve Jobs,' Based On Walter Isaacson Book For Sony |last=Fleming Jr |first=Mike |publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |date=2012-05-15 |accessdate=2016-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160704102342/http://deadline.com/2012/05/aaron-sorkin-to-script-steve-jobs-based-on-walter-isaacson-book-for-sony-272953/ |archive-date=2016-07-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並獲得蘋果公司的聯合創辦人[[史蒂夫·沃茲尼克|史蒂夫·沃茲尼克]]的協助，使劇本在歷史準確性方面增色不少<ref name="Jordan Zakarin">{{cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/apple-founder-steve-wozniak-hired-aaron-sorkin-steve-jobs-326595 |title=Apple Co-Founder Steve Wozniak Hired to Help Aaron Sorkin on Steve Jobs Biopic |last=Zakarin |first=Jordan |work=[[好萊塢報導|The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=2012-05-18 |accessdate=2016-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310173406/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/apple-founder-steve-wozniak-hired-aaron-sorkin-steve-jobs-326595 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。索金隨後表示，他的劇本將包含三幕，每幕時長30分鐘，涵蓋賈伯斯16年的人生<ref>{{cite web |first=Kevin |last=Jagernauth |url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/aaron-sorkin-talks-181-page-jobs-script-says-about-100-of-it-is-that-one-character-20141118 |title=Aaron Sorkin Talks 181-Page 'Jobs' Script, Says "About 100 Of It Is That One Character" |publisher=[[Indiewire|Indiewire]] |date=2014-11-18 |accessdate=2016-08-26 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiewire.com%2F2014%2F11%2Faaron-sorkin-talks-181-page-jobs-script-says-about-100-of-it-is-that-one-character-269994%2F&date=2014-11-18 |archive-date=2014-11-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |first=Bryan |last=Bishop |url=http://www.theverge.com/2014/12/11/7376435/this-is-how-excited-david-fincher-was-about-the-steve-jobs-movie |title=This is how excited David Fincher was about the Steve Jobs movie |work=[[The_Verge|The Verge]] |date=2014-12-11 |accessdate=2014-12-11 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2014%2F12%2F11%2F7376435%2Fthis-is-how-excited-david-fincher-was-about-the-steve-jobs-movie&date=2016-08-31 |archive-date=2016-08-31 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |first=Peter |last=Sciretta |url=http://www.slashfilm.com/steve-jobs-movie-flashbacks |title=Is Danny Boyle's ''Steve Jobs'' Still Set Primarily During Three Keynotes? |publisher=slashfilm.com |date=2015-01-27 |accessdate=2015-01-30 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.slashfilm.com%2Fsteve-jobs-movie-flashbacks&date=2016-08-31 |archive-date=2016-08-31 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

索金發展了圍繞賈伯斯及幾名關鍵人物間關係的劇本：蘋果公司的聯合創始人史蒂夫·沃茲尼克、賈伯斯的「左右手」{{link-en|喬安娜·霍夫曼|Joanna Hoffman}}<ref name="dbprem"/>、前蘋果公司CEO[[約翰·史考利|約翰·史考利]]、{{link-en|Macintosh 128K|Macintosh 128K}}團隊的成員[[安迪·赫茲菲爾德|安迪·赫茲菲爾德]]、賈伯斯的第一個兒女[[麗薩·布倫南-賈伯斯|麗薩·布倫南-賈伯斯]]以及麗莎的母親{{link-en|克里斯安·布倫南|Chrisann Brennan}}<ref name="dbprem">{{cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/sep/06/steve-jobs-movie-danny-boyle-kate-winslet-seth-rogen-aaron-sorkin |title=Danny Boyle on Steve Jobs: movies must be made about powerful men |accessdate=2016-08-26 |last=Shoard |first=Catherine |date=2015-09-06 |work=[[衛報|The Guardian]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160824073945/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/sep/06/steve-jobs-movie-danny-boyle-kate-winslet-seth-rogen-aaron-sorkin |archive-date=2016-08-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。索金在寫劇本時與所有人進行會談，包含麗莎（在艾薩克森撰寫《賈伯斯傳》時並未與艾薩克森會談）。但索金也已表示，許多對白都是虛構的<ref name="dbprem" />。

