1160356%2F&date=2016-09-01 |archive-date=2016-09-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。10月，迪卡皮歐退出，貝爾、[[麥特·戴蒙|麥特·戴蒙]]、[[班·艾佛列克|班·艾佛列克]]與[[布萊德利·庫柏|布萊德利·庫柏]]皆為考慮人選<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/leonardo-dicaprio-exits-steve-jobs-737570 |title=Leonardo DiCaprio Exits Steve Jobs Biopic as Contenders Line Up (Exclusive) |last1=Siegel |first1=Tatiana |first2=Borys |last2=Kit |work=[[好萊塢報導|The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=2014-10-02 |accessdate=2014-12-29 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hollywoodreporter.com%2Fnews%2Fleonardo-dicaprio-exits-steve-jobs-737570&date=2016-09-01 |archive-date=2016-09-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。索金在10月接受採訪時透露，貝爾再次成為了該角色的演員，[[塞斯·羅根|塞斯·羅根]]正為飾演沃茲尼克一角而談判中，而[[潔西卡·崔絲坦|潔西卡·崔絲坦]]則考慮加入演員行列<ref>{{cite news |url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/seth-rogen-steve-wozniak-steve-jobs-biopic-1201338038/ |title=Seth Rogen to Play Apple Co-Founder Wozniak in Steve Jobs Biopic |work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]] |first=Dave |last=McNary |date=2014-10-30 |accessdate=2014-12-29 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2014%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fseth-rogen-steve-wozniak-steve-jobs-biopic-1201338038%2F&date=2016-09-01 |archive-date=2016-09-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[伊克·巴里霍爾茨|伊克·巴里霍爾茨]]透露，他曾為沃茲尼克一角試鏡<ref>{{cite web |last=Barna |first=Ben |url=http://bullettmedia.com/article/perfect-casting-news-christian-bale-will-play-steve-jobs/ |title=Christian Bale Will Play Steve Jobs in Aaron Sorkin Biopic |website=BulletMedia |date=2014-10-15 |accessdate=2015-11-01 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fbullettmedia.com%2Farticle%2Fperfect-casting-news-christian-bale-will-play-steve-jobs%2F&date=2016-09-01 |archive-date=2016-09-01 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。11月，貝爾再次退出<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/christian-bale-exits-steve-jobs-745784 |title=Christian Bale Exits Steve Jobs Movie (Exclusive) |last1=Kit |first1=Borys |last2=Siegel |first2=Tatiana |work=[[好萊塢報導|Th