為了區分電影中描繪的三種產品，丹尼·鮑伊和攝影師{{link-en|阿爾文·H·卡克勒|Alwin H. Küchler}}採用了三種不同的電影格式：1984年時以{{link-en|16毫米膠片|16 mm film}}規格拍攝，1988年時以[[35毫米膠片|35毫米膠片]]規格拍攝，而1998年時則以[[阿萊Alexa|阿萊Alexa]]數位電影攝影機拍攝。他們還希望，電影中的每個時間點能反映出賈伯斯當時自身的發展。例如，卡克勒解釋說，在德安薩學院的弗林特中心拍攝第一幕時，以16毫米膠片的顆粒感來強調臨時自發的外觀。第三幕在路易斯·M·戴維斯交響樂廳以阿萊Alexa拍攝，結合了美學和色澤，呈現賈伯斯對自己的iMac和之後的蘋果硬體的設計理念。卡克勒表示，他拍攝《史蒂夫賈伯斯》是一次「輝煌且富挑戰性」的經歷，並指出他的目標是「確保視覺效果能跟上對白」<ref name="boylewired">{{cite web |url=https://www.wired.com/2015/10/steve-jobs-danny-boyle-interview/ |title=Why Danny Boyle Filmed Steve Jobs in Three Different Formats |work=[[連線|Wired]] |date=2015-10-16 |accessdate=2015-11-17 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2F2015%2F10%2Fsteve-jobs-danny-boyle-interview%2F&date=2016-09-03 |archive-date=2016-09-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="kuchlerthalo">{{cite web |url=http://www.thalo.com/articles/view/1143/steve_jobs_dp_alwin_h_kchler_shoots_in_three_acts |title=Steve Jobs DP Alwin H. Küchler Shoots in Three Acts |last=Blum |first=Laura |publisher=Thalo |date=2015-10-09 |accessdate=2015-11-17 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thalo.com%2Farticles%2Fview%2F1143%2Fsteve_jobs_dp_alwin_h_kchler_shoots_in_three_acts&date=2016-09-03 |archive-date=2016-09-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="kuchlermpcg">{{cite web |url=http://motionpicturecameragear.com/interview-steve-jobs-director-of-photography-alwin-kuchler |title='Steve Jobs' Director of Photography Alwin Küchler (profile) |publisher=Motion Picture Camera Gear |accessdate=2015-11-17 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fmotionpicturecameragear.com%2Finterview-steve-jobs-director-of-photography-alwin-kuchler&date=2016-09-03 |archive-date=2016-09-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="boyleindiewire">{{cite web |url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/thompsononhollywood/how-they-shot-steve-jobs-from-inside-out-with-three-different-looks-20151009 |title=How They Shot 'Steve Jobs' from Inside Out with Three Different Looks |last=Desowitz |first=Bill |publisher=[[Indiewire|Indiewire]] |date=2015-10-09 |accessdate=2015-11-17 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fblogs.indiewire.com%2Fthompsononhollywood%2Fhow-they-shot-steve-jobs-from-inside-out-with-three-different-looks-20151009&date=2016-09-03 |archive-date=2016-09-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="hrkuchler">{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/behind-screen/steve-jobs-cinematographer-explains-visual-847406 |title='Steve Jobs' Cinematographer Explains Visual Transitions In the Three-Act Film |first=Carolyn |last=Giardina |work=[[好萊塢報導|The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=2015-12-09 |accessdate=2015-12-10 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hollywoodreporter.com%2Fbehind-screen%2Fsteve-jobs-cinematographer-explains-visual-847406&date=2016-09-03 |archive-date=2016-09-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 後期製作 ===

倫敦基礎工作室聯盟負責製作電影的[[視覺效果|視覺效果]]<ref>{{cite web |last=Rosser |first=Michael |url=http://www.screendaily.com/news/union-to-handle-vfx-on-danny-boyles-steve-jobs-biopic/5083638.article?blocktitle=Most-popular&contentID=-1 |title=Union to handle VFX on Danny Boyle's Steve Jobs biopic |publisher={{link-en|國際銀幕|Screen International|ScreenDaily.com}} |date=2015-02-26 |accessdate=2015-03-03 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6kE6YBsof?url=http://www.screendaily.com/news/union-to-handle-vfx-on-danny-boyles-steve-jobs-biopic/5083638.article?blocktitle=Most-popular |archive-date=2016-09-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。根據剪輯師{{link-en|艾略特·葛拉罕|Elliot Graham}}的說法，多數的剪輯作業都是在主要攝影結束後進行。在為期一週排演期間，葛拉罕在現有素材上進行處理，並持續於編輯室中接獲鮑伊的反饋。葛拉罕在接受《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]》雜誌採訪時表示，他的一個特別挑戰是平衡拍攝的頻率，並加入足夠的「視覺干擾」來掌控索金劇本中沉重的對白的部分。他將大半場景描述成「一連串的戰鬥場景」。麥可·法斯賓達提供了多種他飾演賈伯斯的版本，供葛拉罕和鮑伊在[[後期製作|後期製作]]中進行挑選<ref name="boylecrave">{{cite web |url=http://www.craveonline.com/culture/912765-interview-danny-boyle-politics-steve-jobs |title=Interview Danny Boyle on the Politics of ''Steve Jobs'' |last=Bibbiani |first=William |publisher={{link-en|CraveOnline|CraveOnline}} |date=2015-10-16 |accessdate=2015-11-17 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.craveonline.com%2Fculture%2F912765-interview-danny-boyle-politics-steve-jobs&date=2016-09-02 |archive-date=2016-09-02 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="grahamguild">{{cite web |url=https://www.editorsguild.com/FromTheGuild.cfm?FromTheGuildid=535 |title=From the Guild: Getting to the Core of Apple |last=Feld |first=Rob |publisher={{link-en|電影剪輯協會|Motion Picture Editors Guild|Motion Picture Editors Guild}} |date=2015-11-04 |accessdate=2015-11-17 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.editorsguild.com%2FFromTheGuild.cfm%3FFromTheGuildid%3D535&date=2016-09-02 |archive-date=2016-09-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/video/steve-jobs-editing-aaron-sorkin/ |title=Steve Jobs Editor on the Rush of Working With Aaron Sorkin Dialogue |work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]] |accessdate=2015-11-17 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fvideo%2Fsteve-jobs-editing-aaron-sorkin%2F&date=2016-09-02 |archive-date=2016-09-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。葛拉罕還表示，「丹尼會參與其中，但同時也需要耗掉一些時間。他會說：『如果我和你共事，我們總是會出現相同的意見，因為我們走的是一模一樣的旅程』」<ref name="FilmDoctor">{{cite web |url=http://filmdoctor.co.uk/2015/12/08/steve-jobs-editor-elliot-graham-in-conversation/ |title='Steve Jobs' Elliot Graham in conversation |last=Wooding |first=Andy |publisher=Film Doctor |date=2015-12-08 |accessdate=2015-12-08 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Ffilmdoctor.co.uk%2F2015%2F12%2F08%2Fsteve-jobs-editor-elliot-graham-in-conversation%2F&date=2016-09-02 |archive-date=2016-09-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

